OL,3,CDrug dealer was on licence from prison
OL,4,Cwhen he killed woman, trial told
OL,6,FA drug dealer who stamped on a 56-year-
OL,7,Fold mother, causing fatal brain
OL,8,Finjuries in a random attack in
OL,9,FLeicester, had been released from
OL,10,Fprison on licence a year earlier, a
OL,11,Fmurder trial has heard.
OL,13,FLeicester Crown Court was told former
OL,14,Funiversity student Chukwuemeka Ahanonu
OL,15,Fwas freed from a two-year sentence in
OL,16,FJuly 2024, having been found with more
OL,17,Fthan #1,000 in cash and a machete
OL,18,Fafter going through a red light in
OL,19,FSeptember 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
