FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773162679
OL,3,CDrug dealer was on licence from prison
OL,4,Cwhen he killed woman, trial told
OL,6,FProsecutors allege Ahanonu, 23,
OL,7,Fmurdered Nila Patel near Leicester
OL,8,FRoyal Infirmary in a vicious attack
OL,9,Fcaused by his use of cannabis on 24
OL,10,FJune last year.
OL,12,FAhanonu, originally from Peckham in
OL,13,Fsouth-east London, has admitted
OL,14,Fmanslaughter but denies murder,
OL,15,Fclaiming diminished responsibility for
OL,16,Fthe killing.
OL,18,FMs Patel, who got off a bus after
OL,19,FAhanonu crashed and overturned a BMW,
OL,20,Fdied in hospital two days after
OL,21,Fsuffering brain damage.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773162679
OL,3,CDrug dealer was on licence from prison
OL,4,Cwhen he killed woman, trial told
OL,6,FIn agreed facts read to the jury on
OL,7,FMonday by junior prosecution counsel
OL,8,FCaroline Bray, it was also stated that
OL,9,Fa blood test for cannabis showed
OL,10,FAhanonu was almost four times the
OL,11,Flegal limit for driving.
OL,13,FMs Bray said it was agreed between the
OL,14,Fprosecution and the defence that no
OL,15,Falcohol was found in a blood sample
OL,16,Ftaken around three hours after the
OL,17,Falleged murder.
OL,19,FBut a test for THC, which is produced
OL,20,Fby cannabis use, found a level of
OL,21,F7.6mcg, above the limit of 2mcg.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773162679
OL,3,CDrug dealer was on licence from prison
OL,4,Cwhen he killed woman, trial told
OL,6,FMs Bray told the court Ahanonu, of
OL,7,FDover Street, Leicester, was given a
OL,8,Fsuspended sentence in June 2023 after
OL,9,Fbeing convicted of possession with
OL,10,Fintent to supply cannabis at his
OL,11,Funiversity flat.
OL,13,FThe court heard his car was then
OL,14,Fstopped by police in August 2023 and
OL,15,Fagain in September 2023, with officers
OL,16,Ffinding a machete and cannabis during
OL,17,Fthe second stop.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773162679
OL,3,CDrug dealer was on licence from prison
OL,4,Cwhen he killed woman, trial told
OL,6,FAhanonu was charged and remanded in
OL,7,Fcustody and later received a 24-month
OL,8,Fjail sentence for offences including
OL,9,Fpossession of a bladed article and
OL,10,Fbreaching a suspended sentence order.
OL,12,FConfirming that Ahanonu was on licence
OL,13,Fat the time Ms Patel was attacked, Ms
OL,14,FBray told jurors: "His licence began
OL,15,Fon his release from custody on July 19
OL,16,F2024. It was due to end on September
OL,17,F20 2025."
OL,26,@vD@SOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773162679
OL,3,CDrug dealer was on licence from prison
OL,4,Cwhen he killed woman, trial told
OL,6,FThe conditions of the licence, Ms Bray
OL,7,Fsaid, were for Ahanonu "to be of good
OL,8,Fbehaviour", not to commit any offence,
OL,9,Fnot to possess more than one
OL,10,Ftelephone, and to live at an approved
OL,11,Faddress.
OL,13,FIn relation to the events on the day
OL,14,FMs Patel was fatally injured, the
OL,15,Fcourt heard, Ahanonu has admitted
OL,16,Fdangerous driving, possession of
OL,17,Fcannabis with intent to supply and
OL,18,Fassaulting an emergency worker.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773162679
OL,3,CDrug dealer was on licence from prison
OL,4,Cwhen he killed woman, trial told
OL,6,F"He has also pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fmanslaughter on the basis he asserts
OL,8,Fhe has a partial defence to murder of
OL,9,Fdiminished responsibility," Ms Bray
OL,10,Ftold the court.
OL,12,FFollowing the end of the Crown's case,
OL,13,FAhanonu opted not to give evidence in
OL,14,Fhis defence.
OL,16,FAt the start of Ahanonu's case, which
OL,17,Fis expected to hear psychiatric
OL,18,Fevidence, defence KC Paul Raudnitz
OL,19,Ftold Judge Timothy Spencer KC that the
OL,20,Fdefendant will not be giving evidence
OL,21,Fto the jury.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773162679
OL,3,CDrug dealer was on licence from prison
OL,4,Cwhen he killed woman, trial told
OL,6,FThe judge then asked the defence
OL,7,Fbarrister if Ahanonu had been advised
OL,8,Fthat refusal to give evidence may lead
OL,9,Fjurors to "draw such inferences as are
OL,10,Fproper" from his failure to do so.
OL,12,FMr Raudnitz replied: "I have advised
OL,13,Fhim of that."
OL,15,FThe trial continues.
OL,26,@qD@KOUrD@GO]tD@VOUuD@MO]
